reviewText: Not bad. Only one movie is just bad. Dumb movie.
All pretty good. Interesting Chet Baker music in Playin By Heart very good
I only liked one of the four!

Bought this just for the movie 'Playing by Heart'.  Great ensemble cast, I will never understand why it was not more popular when it came out.  Lack of violence and car chases may have something to do with it.  I can tell you nothing about the other 2 movies, sorry.
I enjoyed Four Rooms and 2 other movies in this package. Jennifer Beals was wonderful in Four Rooms. She should of had more of  a greater role.

I love Playing By Heart & Four Rooms so I purchased this DVD thinking the other two films would become favorites too. I couldn't even get through Full Frontal, I was bored to tears; Beautiful Girls was tolerable only because Rosy ODonnell was hilarious & made it bearable to get thru.
